children.subject: I think you shouldn't have trouble getting approved. I've heard of it being done before.

history.content: Hello I was just wondering the likelihood of this petition being accepted. I am currently in physics 89 and want to use it to satisfy math54 requirement so I can move on to 16B as ASAP. Is this petition possible. Physics 89 covers the same information as math54 plus some more, so I think it would be unfair not to accept it as a substitute. Thanks
history.subject: Petition for Physics 89 to count for math 54/16A requirement.
